title: CurrentStructureFeaturePacket
description: Informs the client of which Structure Feature they are currently occupying.

Current Structure Feature.description: The identifier of the Structure Feature that the player is currently occupying. If the player is not occupying a structure then this value is an empty string.

$metaProperties.[cereal:packet_details]:
Sends the name of the Structure Feature the player is currently occupying to the client.
	If the player is not in a structure, this packet contains an empty string.
